Version 1.0, February 2011

This repository contains pipeline scripts and tooling that wrap FreeSurfer,
SynthSR, SynthSeg, and FastSurfer. Use of this software is subject to the
FreeSurfer Software License Agreement reproduced below, which governs use of
the underlying tools. The wrapper code (shell scripts, Python TUI) is made
available under the same non-commercial research terms.

