Third-Party Tools

This pipeline invokes the following tools, each governed by its own license:

  FreeSurfer   https://surfer.nmr.mgh.harvard.edu/fswiki/FreeSurferSoftwareLicense
  SynthSR      https://github.com/BBillot/SynthSR  (Apache-2.0)
  SynthSeg     https://github.com/BBillot/SynthSeg (Apache-2.0)
  FastSurfer   https://github.com/Deep-MI/FastSurfer (Apache-2.0)

A valid FreeSurfer license file (license.txt) is required to run SynthSR and
FastSurfer. Register at: https://surfer.nmr.mgh.harvard.edu/registration.html
